---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="Privacy policy \u2014 Harmony Threads" description="How Harmony Threads collects, stores, and uses your personal information.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 md:px-8 py-16">
    <h1 class="font-display text-5xl">Privacy</h1>
    <div class="mt-6 space-y-6 text-paper/80 leading-relaxed">
      <p>We collect only what we need to fulfil your order and send you the newsletter if you ask for it. We do not sell your data. Ever.</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl">What we store</h2>
      <p>Your email, shipping address, and order history are stored in our Supabase database. Card details are never stored by us \u2014 they are handled by Stripe, a PCI-DSS Level 1 payment processor.</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl">Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use a single first-party cookie to keep your cart alive between visits. No third-party tracking, no ad pixels.</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl">Your rights</h2>
      <p>Email <a href="mailto:privacy@harmonythreads.shop" class="text-amber underline">privacy@harmonythreads.shop</a> to request a copy or deletion of your data. We process requests within 30 days.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
